description: Dominik Trojan, Marcio Gonzales and Dario Dolce - Boris and Enzo go to the local bar for a bottle of wine and soon witness an arousing floor show put on by Marcio and Dario. The two horndogs carry on unashamedly, soon joined by barkeep Domink Trojan who knows how to shake his stick, shoving it high up into the boys' primed asscracks.
title: Czech Tales, Part 1
